<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <!-- width: device-width로 브라우저의 너비를 모바일 기기의 width로 지정함,initial-scale: 1은 100%를 뜻함 즉 사이트의 줌을 바꾸지 않는다 -->
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>하네스사이즈체크입력</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div class ="container">
        <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-6">
        <form action="/petinfo/harness" method="POST" class="signupform">
            
        <legend>반려견의 정보를 입력해주세요</legend>
        <legend>반려견의 하네스사이즈를 체크할수있습니다</legend>

        <div class="form-group"></div>
        <label for="name">견주이름</label>
        <input name="name" type="text" class="form-control"  minlength="2" placeholder="견주이름">

        <div class="form-group"></div>
        <label for="dogname">강아지이름</label>
        <input name="dogname" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="강아지이름">
        
        <div class="form-group"></div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">입력하기</button>
        <input type="button"  onclick=" location.href='/petinfo/list'" class="btn btn-primary"  value="이전으로"/>
        </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
</body>